Description: The Global Collaboratory on the History of Labour Relations uses a pre-formatted excel file to input data  (see http://www.historyoflabourrelations.org). Lar allows you to (1) easily read in this pre-formatted excel data, and (2) also allows you to visualisize labour relations as treemaps according to the Collaboratory's suggested format (e.g. in relation to colours and positioning of leaves).
Imports: data.table, grid, treemap, xlsx
